snippet.title: Champions Tactics – Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Champions Tactics™ Grimoria Chronicles is an upcoming PVP Tactical RPG game on PC currently in development at Ubisoft. 

Assemble a team of mythical Champions, engage in thrilling tactical battles against other players and discover the legends of the dark and mystical world of Grimoria. 

Follow us on our social networks and subscribe to our newsletter to stay in touch with the latest news.

Website - https://championstactics.com
Twitter - https://twitter.com/championsverse
Discord - Private
